{
  "texts": [
    "• Some studies considered only commercial SIEM solutions for evaluation, which are suitable only for large enterprises due to huge licensing costs.",
    "• Another group of research studies provided theoretical comparisons of open-source SIEM solutions but the experimental evaluation of their performance and security features is not performed.",
    "• Others have performed experimental evaluation, but only for a single SIEM solution in isolation, which does not provide a head-to-head comparison of various SIEMs.",
    "Comparison of related work.",
    "Ref Wazuh OSSIM SIEMonster Elastic Security A1 A2 A3 Safarzadeh et al. [34] χ ✓ χ χ ✓ χ χ Christopher et al."
